<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Delivery Status Update</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      color: #333;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2ecc71; /* Green color indicating delivered status */
    }
    p {
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    .order-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .order-id {
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .order-status {
      color: #2ecc71; /* Green color for delivered status */
    }
    .delivery-partner {
      color: #3498db; /* Blue color for delivery partner */
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .rating-section {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .rating-section a {
      color: #3498db; /* Blue color for the link */
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Your Order Has Been Delivered!</h1>
    <p>Great news! Your order has been successfully delivered to you!</p>

    <div class="order-details">
      <p class="order-id">Order ID: <%= @order.id %></p>
      <p class="order-status">Status: <strong>Delivered</strong></p>
      <p>If you need to contact the delivery partner for any reason, here are their details:</p>
      <p class="delivery-partner">Delivery Partner: <%= @rider.phone %></p>
    </div>

    <p>We hope you are enjoying your order! If you have any issues or feedback, feel free to reach out to us.</p>

    <div class="rating-section">
      <p>Your feedback is important to us!</p>
      <p>Please take a moment to rate your experience with us.</p>
      <p><a href="<%= "/reviews/new?pid=#{@order.payment.payment_intent_id}&r_id=#{@order.dish.restaurant.id}" %>">Click here to rate your order and provide feedback</a></p> 
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for choosing us. We look forward to serving you again soon!</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
